title: Genesis Live Knebworth 1992 full concert XviD PreTV HiFi stereo
description: Pre-broadcast version of Genesis Live at Knebworth 2nd August 1992, this is an original transfer direct from a master 1992 VHS recording taken direct from the video/audio feed at the venue, never before released with some extra pre-concert footage, this is not the same as other versions available. Video is VHS with no channel logo, audio is Hi-Fi stereo with no broadcast compression. Duration 2h 29m 29s
